trans-unit.source: Defines a static <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ClientRemotingConfig.Write*> method that creates a client remoting configuration file for a client type library.
trans-unit.target: Definierar en statisk <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ClientRemotingConfig.Write*>metod som skapar en klient fjärrkommunikation konfigurationsfil för en klient typbiblioteket.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ClientRemotingConfig.Write*>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ClientRemotingConfig.Write%2A> method is used by the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish> class while generating a COM interface from a client type library (with a .tlb extension).
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ClientRemotingConfig.Write%2A>metoden används av den <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish>klassen när ett COM-gränssnitt från en klient typbiblioteket (med filtillägget .tlb).</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish> </xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ClientRemotingConfig.Write%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish> class publishes COM interfaces in a SOAP-enabled COM+ application.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish>klassen publicerar COM-gränssnitt i SOAP-aktiverade COM +-programmet.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish>

trans-unit.source: One of the method's parameters is the name of an assembly that contains common language runtime (CLR) metadata that <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish> has already generated for the client type library.
trans-unit.target: En av metodens parametrar är namnet på en sammansättning som innehåller common language runtime (CLR) metadata som <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish>redan har genererats för klienten typbiblioteket.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ClientRemotingConfig.Write%2A> does not need to be called directly.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ClientRemotingConfig.Write%2A>behöver inte anropas direkt.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ClientRemotingConfig.Write%2A>

trans-unit.source: Instead, call the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish.ProcessClientTlb%2A> method of the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish> class.
trans-unit.target: Istället anropa <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish.ProcessClientTlb%2A>metoden i <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish>klassen.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish> </xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish.ProcessClientTlb%2A>

trans-unit.source: ClientRemotingConfig is used internally by the .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: ClientRemotingConfig används internt av .NET Framework.

trans-unit.source: You do not need to use the class directly in your code.
trans-unit.target: Du behöver inte använda klassen direkt i din kod.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ClientRemotingConfig"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.ClientRemotingConfig"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Creates a client remoting configuration file for a client type library in a SOAP-enabled COM+ application.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en klient fjärrkommunikation konfigurationsfil för ett typbibliotek för klienten i SOAP-aktiverade COM +-programmet.

trans-unit.source: The static Write method is called by the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish> class while generating a COM interface from a client type library (with a .tlb extension).
trans-unit.target: Den statiska Write-metoden anropas av den <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish>klassen när ett COM-gränssnitt från en klient typbiblioteket (med filtillägget .tlb).</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish> class publishes COM interfaces in a SOAP-enabled COM+ application.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish>klassen publicerar COM-gränssnitt i SOAP-aktiverade COM +-programmet.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish>

trans-unit.source: Write does not need to be called directly.
trans-unit.target: Skriv behöver inte anropas direkt.

trans-unit.source: Instead, call the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish.ProcessClientTlb%2A> method of the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish> class.
trans-unit.target: Istället anropa <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish.ProcessClientTlb%2A>metoden i <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish>klassen.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish> </xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish.ProcessClientTlb%2A>

trans-unit.source: The `BaseUrl` and `VRoot` parameter values are concatenated (with a path separator, if needed) to form the client element's `URL` attribute value.
trans-unit.target: Den `BaseUrl` och `VRoot` parametervärden sammanfogas (med en sökväg avgränsare, om det behövs) till formuläret klientelementet `URL` attributvärdet.

trans-unit.source: The `AssemblyName` parameter identifies an assembly containing CLR metadata that <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish>, using the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.GenerateMetadata> class, has already generated for the client type library.
trans-unit.target: Den `AssemblyName` parametern identifierar en sammansättning som innehåller CLR-metadata som <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish>med hjälp av den <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.GenerateMetadata>klassen, har redan genererat för klienten typbiblioteket.</xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.GenerateMetadata> </xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish>
